### Escaping XML in Edits

When editing files that contain `<search>`, `<edit>`, or similar XML-like tags,
use `escape="html"` and write the content with HTML entities:

```
&lt;edit file="prompts.py" escape="html"&gt;
&lt;search&gt;
text with &amp;lt;search&amp;gt; tags
&lt;/search&gt;
&lt;replace&gt;
